  <Strings>
    <Section>Main</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42412</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_001&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君たちは……エルフでは
ないようだが……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You guys aren't elves, are you?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42488</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_002&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>はい、違いますけど……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>We aren't, why do you ask...?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42620</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_003&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>魔術を使えるのはエルフだけのはずだ。
でも、君たちは魔術を使える。どうしてだ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Only those with elven blood can use magic...but you can use magic anyways. Why's that?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42684</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_004&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>えっと……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Well...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42780</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_005&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>そこが『なりきり士』の
すごいところだぜ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>That's because of how amazing it is to be a "Roleplayer"!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>42912</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_006&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>エルフでもないのに魔術を、か。
『なりきり士』っていうのは得体の知れない力だな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You aren't elves but can use magic, huh? The power of "Roleplaying" sounds quite surreal.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43056</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_007&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>あっ、もしかして料理人の服着れば、超一流の
すげーうまい豪華料理を作って食えるんじゃねーの？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh yeah! Does that mean if we got some chef's clothes we would be able to prepare the best dishes ever?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43164</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_008&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>大工さんになったら、
エトスハウスを新しく建て直せるかも</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Or if you were a carpenter we could turn Ethos' House into a huge mansion!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>4</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43256</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_009&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>家の修理も、豪華料理も
材料が必要だよ？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Big meals and a great house are all you really want?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>2</SpeakerId>
      <Id>9</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43328</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_010&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>君はリアリストだな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You're pretty down to the ground.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>1</SpeakerId>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset>43408</PointerOffset>
      <VoiceId>&lt;audio:VCT_001_018_011&gt;</VoiceId>
      <JapaneseText>っていうか、
夢がないぜ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...So you say. Now the dream has died.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>3</SpeakerId>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
